{"tid":2389580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葉劉：純粹因BNO問題入籍英國的移民 只會是難民","createTime":"2021-02-01T04:19:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T09:38:28.000Z","uid":184679,"like":7,"dislike":66,"uniUserReply":97,"replies":[{"pid":"1d14e10900ad75c12adef84f6e8ef0b38e2753d5","tid":2389580,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T04:19:01.000Z","msg":"葉劉淑儀估計，一些曾參與騷亂事件，或擔心違反國安法被捕的人，都已離開香港；現時仍計劃移民的港人，並不單純因為國安法，而會考慮香港是否出現經濟下滑、無前景，或希望子女接受英式教育等問題。 葉劉淑儀表示，對當地文化歷史不熟悉的港人移民，即使入籍英國，都可能會被歧視，純粹因為BNO問題獲批的移民，只會是難民。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hkcna.hk/content/2021/0201/U611P22T1D876931F1DT20210201111332.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcna.hk%2Fcontent%2F2021%2F0201%2FU611P22T1D876931F1DT20210201111332.JPG&h=07c13b24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">http://www.hkcna. hk/content/2021/0201/876931.shtml</code></pre>"},{"pid":"598e8f82aa38b2672cefd3489c3aaea52711b91a","tid":2389580,"uid":79563,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T04:21:35.000Z","msg":"不斷出口術, <br />\n<br />\n只係示弱表現"},{"pid":"027545e24ef5be1c533749dbe23f173c29b256e0","tid":2389580,"uid":152476,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T04:22:11.000Z","msg":"得啦得啦<br />\n又難民又二等公民<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"357f761ababa089389618be6268b7223ac0ce6d3","tid":2389580,"uid":22450,"like":68,"dislike":0,"score":68,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T04:22:48.000Z","msg":"見二等公民個term 唔work就改做難民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e20415551aa1a5800d833aaae9e914bddf1192e6","tid":2389580,"uid":184787,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T04:24:02.000Z","msg":"問下你阿妹個仔有無比人歧視先？"},{"pid":"72744920c6d0144f6a6e317c90b00bfb422c9d64","tid":2389580,"uid":11291,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T04:25:20.000Z","msg":"咁譚耀宗個仔算唔算係澳洲難民"},{"pid":"c010e484d9d28bb761562f259c8747b1d74c50ad","tid":2389580,"uid":184679,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T04:27:17.000Z","msg":"葉劉淑儀的父親是新加坡華人，早年在當地的英華學校受教，後來興辦貿易公司「有裕行」，與中國共產黨關係密切[4]。葉劉淑儀出生之時，適值韓戰爆發，其父生意損失慘重。在家道中落的情況下，她四歲左右舉家由巴丙頓道的3,000平方呎大宅搬到般咸道的400平方呎單位[14]。劉福成晚年主要居於新加坡，1971年在那裡因肺癌病逝。至於華彩鳳則長居香港，後於1990年元旦在香港因腸癌病逝[12]。<br />\n<br />\n葉劉淑儀另有一名胞弟，名劉德麟（1953年－2002年），在菲律賓當風水師。兩人甚少聯絡，他於2002年3月因心臟病突發在菲律賓病逝[12]。<br />\n<br />\n（維基百科）"},{"pid":"9e6894b48b6e49efb21e40ec45875266c2599a99","tid":2389580,"uid":22553,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T04:28:25.000Z","msg":"比黑警歧視叫咩民<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9ebcf23346c69a97ca3980f37d9fca47852ee90","tid":2389580,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T04:29:03.000Z","msg":"劏豬櫈"},{"pid":"7c3fe3703938ac303cc96e8e15f546ce863ee488","tid":2389580,"uid":22700,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T04:29:19.000Z","msg":"出自佢地呢D屋企人有英藉既人把口真係好有趣"},{"pid":"c08892c54670787ad7ab869bd85c948375f03acf","tid":2389580,"uid":327169,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T04:29:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關你咩事，人哋就算做難民都開心過留喺香港，唔信咪問吓林鄭月娥"},{"pid":"d10bf369ecab86d41a3f2615887bb0622c0d4a80","tid":2389580,"uid":34641,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T04:30:18.000Z","msg":"二等公民 難民<br />\n仲會唔會再差啲嘅terms<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77f55af56b2fccef7fb431f91ac8deb1a90702c6","tid":2389580,"uid":156542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T04:31:05.000Z","msg":"係都要衝出嚟柒嘅"},{"pid":"d116c42c5318a230bb087cc994e11bce46411e92","tid":2389580,"uid":304916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T04:31:44.000Z","msg":"老是常出現 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"